  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install the package by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -p1 -i ../jbigkit-2.0-fixes-1.patch &amp;&amp;
sed -e 's/all: lib pbm/all: lib/' \
    -e '/install.*bin/ s/^/#/' \
    -e '/install.*man/ s/^/#/' -i Makefile &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Disable installing the static library:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed -i 's|libjbig/.libs/\*.a||' Makefile</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install &amp;&amp;
chmod -v 755 /usr/lib/libjbig.so</userinput></screen>

    <sect3>
      <title>Command Explanations</title>

      <para>
        <command>sed ...</command>: This command disables building and
        installing file converter programs since it is currently broken.
      </para>

    </sect3>

  </sect2>

